high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room and then turn left to face the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Turn to the right and walk around and face the opposite side of the counter.
Cut the lettuce into slices.
Walk around the bar and across the room to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn to the right and walk around and face the opposite side of the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Walk to the end of the bar and turn left to face the fridge.
Cool the slice of lettuce in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and walk to face the counter.
Place the slice of lettuce beside the knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To cool a slice of lettuce and place it on the counter to the left of the stove.

high_descs: Walk towards the sink counter
Grab a knife from the counter
Walk towards the island counter
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Walk towards the stove counter
Put the knife on the counter
Walk towards the island counter
Grab a slice of lettuce
Walk with the slice towards the fridge
Put the slice of lettuce inside the fridge and take it out
Walk with the slice of lettuce towards the stove counter
Put the slice of lettuce next to the knife
anns.task_desc: Slice the lettuce, take a slice, put it in the fridge put it next to the stove

high_descs: Turn around and cross the kitchen, then turn left and face the drying rack to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the drying rack.
Bring the knife with you and go to the far side of the bar counter so that you are on the same side of it as the stools, then turn left to face it.
Use the knife to cut the head of lettuce on the bar counter.
Bring the knife with you and cross the room, move to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the knife down on the counter in front of the toaster and the salt.
Go back to the spot where you chopped the lettuce on the bar counter.
Pick up a piece of the lettuce.
Carry the lettuce over to the black fridge and face it.
Put the lettuce on the top shelf in the fridge and close the door to let it cool, then take it out again.
Carry the lettuce over to the counter where you left the knife.
Put the lettuce down to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put some cold lettuce on the counter.
